How to deploy werchan on your own site
======================================

1. Follow the werc installation instructions in README
2. Create a cronjob to run bin/prune.rc and delete old threads if you want
3. Rename sites/guhnoo.org to match your domain
4. Edit sites/your_site/_werc/config to your liking
5. Edit sites/your_site/*.html to your liking
6. Add admin accounts to etc/users/ if you want
6. Add admin badges to sites/your_site/team/ if you want
7. Remove or replace the advertisement in sites/your_site/_werc/lib/footer.inc
9. Create boards
   a) Copy sites/your_site/example to sites/your_site/board_name
   b) Edit sites/your_site/board_name/_werc/config
   c) Add board_name to:
        i) bin/prune.rc
       ii) sites/your_site/board_name/_werc/lib/top_bar.inc
      iii) apps/all/index.tpl
